<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَيْرٌ}</span> ... صِحَّةٌ، وَسَعَةُ رِزْقٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فِتْنَةٌ}</span> ... اِبْتِلَاءٌ بِمَكْرُوهٍ وَشِدَّةٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
