<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِسَبَبٍ إِلَى السَّمَاءِ}</span> ... بِحَبْلٍ إِلَى سَقْفِ بَيْتِهِ؛ لْيَخْنُقَ بِهِ نَفْسَهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ثُمَّ لِيَقْطَعْ}</span> ...<span class="c5"> أَيْ:</span> لِيَقْطَعْ ذَلِكَ الحَبْلَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
